1 thereof. This fee structure may be reviewed in fiscal year 2007-08.
2 (4) The Beginning in fiscal year 2007-08, the department shall
3 annually review and adjust the fee structure in this section and section
4 54-2423 to ensure that fees are adequate to meet thirty twenty percent of
